# Byline monorepo structure
# 
# Core components:
# - contract/        Smart contract (Soroban/Rust)
# - reader-app/      Reader frontend (React/TypeScript)
# - publisher-backend/ Publisher backend (Express/TypeScript)
# - publisher-sdk/   Publisher SDK (TypeScript)
#
# This structure enables independent versioning and deployment of each component
# while maintaining a unified development experience.
